{"type":null,"faqId":38509,"title":"备忘录","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">1.</span><a name=\"_task_add_note-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">新建备忘录</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 备忘录”。</span></span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“新建备忘录”，输入记录的内容。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125525\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125526\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 0.22777778in; height: 0.16666667in; vertical-align: text-bottom; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 10.5pt; \">”，插入图片。</span>\n<br>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125527\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">保存备忘录后，您还可以根据屏幕提示进行分享、收藏和删除等操作。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p6\"></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">2.</span><a name=\"_task_set_notepad_options-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">更改备忘录设置</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 备忘录”。</span></span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \